{"tid":2208790,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"白田邨32歲情困男衣架上吊死亡-28歲妻揭發","createTime":"2020-09-19T07:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T13:43:04.000Z","uid":132810,"like":5,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"5b8c19109f468331b54a653a6d85ced503974de8","tid":2208790,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:41:26.000Z","msg":"石硤尾白田邨一名受感情問題困擾的32歲男子，昨日傍晚被妻子發現，在運田樓寓所浴室以衣架上吊死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨晚6時47分接獲事主的28歲妻子報案，指發現丈夫於浴室以衣架上吊。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，消防解下事主，當場被證實死亡。警方於現場沒有檢獲遺書，初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n<br />\n。生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n<br />\n。明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n。東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n<br />\n。社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n<br />\n。香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n<br />\n。撒瑪利亞會熱線（多種語言）︰28960000<br />\n<br />\n。醫院管理局精神健康專線（24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務）：24667350"},{"pid":"be8b4fd3698a2bcecd5b3bb196e1c4d41179ed56","tid":2208790,"uid":73907,"like":92,"dislike":2,"score":90,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:43:55.000Z","msg":"有老婆 但情困 rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b752bd10fbf19871a5d9fa816bfe74ad047f8f11","tid":2208790,"uid":252142,"like":7,"dislike":16,"score":-9,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:44:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c877359b66672aa18fdb441d5d72fdbc9afb7c3a","tid":2208790,"uid":132810,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b752bd10fbf19871a5d9fa816bfe74ad047f8f11","tid":2208790,"uid":252142,"like":7,"dislike":16,"score":-9,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:44:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:45:24.000Z","msg":"見到都下咗聲"},{"pid":"eb1cf5392f04953a34c8f6335daba9dd3a4e3bb5","tid":2208790,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"b752bd10fbf19871a5d9fa816bfe74ad047f8f11","tid":2208790,"uid":252142,"like":7,"dislike":16,"score":-9,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:44:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:45:50.000Z","msg":"拉開個框就吊到。"},{"pid":"340e5f00598213b3dca34bb2ae25